genresAdvancedInfo.name: leon gto indie
genresAdvancedInfo.description: Leon GTO indie is a style of indie rock that emerged in the city of Leon, Mexico. It is known for its energetic and upbeat sound, often featuring catchy guitar riffs and driving rhythms. Leon GTO indie bands often sing in Spanish and draw inspiration from a range of genres, including punk rock, pop, and traditional Mexican music.
